Publish / Publish as PDF

 

The Publish/ Publish as PDF actions give the opportunity to create a new document which can be download. When you select the action, a published revision of the document will be created. The previously published version becomes Obsolete.

 

  • Publish - Manual publish of a document that have been uploaded in the system, so that a locked revision of the document to be created at publish moment. The published version becomes Approved upon publishing the document. The previously published version becomes Obsolete.  Only the content tab is published.

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

  • Publish as PDF - Manual publish of a document that have been created in the system, so that a locked revision of the document to be created at publish moment. The published version becomes Approved upon publishing the document. The previously published version becomes Obsolete. Only the content tab is published.
